WEBVTT

00:01.560 --> 00:03.198
- Previously on Being Human...

00:03.230 --> 00:06.029
- My brother had
a nervous breakdown

00:06.070 --> 00:07.560
and ran away
from his family.

00:07.600 --> 00:08.999
(Roaring)

00:09.040 --> 00:10.906
- Just leave me alone.

00:10.940 --> 00:13.409
- You screw me. You kill me.
You never call.

00:13.440 --> 00:15.807
I can't go to a restaurant
and pretend to be human

00:15.840 --> 00:18.207
when I wanna eat
the table next to me.

00:18.250 --> 00:20.446
- I will be strong
for both of us.

00:20.480 --> 00:22.619
- I lost my engagement ring.

00:22.650 --> 00:27.383
- Why'd you take it off?
- You know I love that ring! (Screaming)

00:27.420 --> 00:29.457
(Crying):
Danny killed me.

00:29.490 --> 00:31.959
(Glass shattering)

00:38.700 --> 00:41.067
(Car horns in distance)

00:41.100 --> 00:44.900
- (Aidan): What sets a human
apart from a monster,

00:44.940 --> 00:46.339
aside from genetics?

00:46.380 --> 00:48.405
Aside from the terrible truth?

00:48.440 --> 00:52.047
We walk the same streets.
We wear the same clothes.

00:52.080 --> 00:53.775
You take a breath,

00:53.820 --> 00:57.586
and there we are,
gulping the same air.

00:57.620 --> 01:00.885
We're walking
in your footsteps.

01:03.730 --> 01:08.258
** Gtill 1 lie silent... *

01:08.300 --> 01:14.899
And even a monster can posses that
most dominant of human emotions...

01:14.940 --> 01:16.704
fear.

01:16.740 --> 01:20.438
We know enough to remember
what we once were.

01:20.480 --> 01:25.509
We know enough to fear
what we can now do.

01:28.150 --> 01:34.089
And, like a human, we
obsess over love, over life,

01:34.120 --> 01:37.181
over every lost cause.

01:42.060 --> 01:45.064
* That kills *

01:45.100 --> 01:49.401
* Fire and soot *

01:49.440 --> 01:52.000
* From an iron flute *

01:52.040 --> 01:57.103
* That shakes the trees
from stem to root **

02:18.600 --> 02:20.762
The Vatican Tweets!

02:22.770 --> 02:25.205
I hate this decade.

02:25.240 --> 02:28.301
(Rattling)

02:30.580 --> 02:31.809
Is that you?

02:32.850 --> 02:33.920
- Sorry.

02:33.950 --> 02:35.975
- How are you doing
that, anyway?

02:36.020 --> 02:37.647
You can't...

02:37.690 --> 02:40.409
- Touch anything, do anything
but make the house shake.

02:40.460 --> 02:41.985
I know.

02:45.990 --> 02:48.152
Maybe because it's mine.

02:49.230 --> 02:51.870
Maybe because it's supposed
to be on my finger.

02:51.900 --> 02:54.995
- But I thought
that Danny took it.

02:56.040 --> 02:57.235
- He did.

02:57.270 --> 02:58.863
- Then how did it get here?

02:58.910 --> 03:04.201
- Aidan, I'm pretty much not gonna
have the answer to any of these questions.

03:06.480 --> 03:08.073
You look nice.

03:08.120 --> 03:10.384
- Is that...
You wearing perfume?

03:16.730 --> 03:19.756
So, it's like
a charged object, right?

03:19.800 --> 03:21.199
- Right.

03:22.970 --> 03:25.120
So I should do
something with it.

03:25.170 --> 03:27.298
- Wait a second. Hold on.

03:27.340 --> 03:29.729
