with Danny, right?

03:32.640 --> 03:34.005
- Am I supposed to be over

03:34.040 --> 03:36.077
the whole wrongful-death
thing by now?

03:36.110 --> 03:38.442
You were the one who said
you'd take care of him.

03:38.480 --> 03:40.448
- Because I didn't wanna
see you get hurt,

03:40.480 --> 03:41.550
Hey, listen to me.

03:41.580 --> 03:43.218
The more involved you get,

03:43.250 --> 03:47.118
