you get in revenge.

03:47.160 --> 03:48.480
(Footsteps approaching)

03:48.520 --> 03:50.784
You will be stuck, Sally.

03:50.830 --> 03:51.979
(Josh sighing)

03:52.030 --> 03:54.499
- Is it picture day
at school?

03:55.630 --> 03:56.597
What's up?

03:56.630 --> 03:58.359
- Nothing...

03:58.400 --> 03:59.731
