05:17.080 --> 05:20.209
- Turn it off!
Turn it off! Whoa!

05:20.250 --> 05:22.116
- There's so much blood!

05:22.150 --> 05:24.812
- (Josh):
What the hell was that?

05:27.720 --> 05:29.927
- Ew, ew, ew! Is that...

05:31.290 --> 05:33.190
