05:33.230 --> 05:35.619
- They get off on this,
don't they?

05:35.660 --> 05:36.968
- Some do.

05:39.800 --> 05:42.508
- So, is it something you like?

05:42.540 --> 05:44.201
- What?

05:44.240 --> 05:45.605
No!

05:45.640 --> 05:46.937
Josh...

05:46.980 --> 05:48.470
No! No.

05:48.510 --> 05:50.444
Someone's just trying
to mess with me.

05:50.480 --> 05:52.039
I will get rid of it.

05:52.080 --> 05:53.616
Don't worry.

05:54.850 --> 05:56.739
- I... I should, um...

05:56.790 --> 05:59.179
I should get to work.

06:02.090 --> 06:03.922
(Josh clears throat)

06:05.160 --> 06:07.151
(Exhales)

06:08.230 --> 06:12.599
** Bring your curtain *

06:12.640 --> 06:14.836
* Down **

06:16.270 --> 06:19.934
- We have the same
weaknesses as you.

06:19.980 --> 06:23.473
But even this
doesn't make us normal.

06:24.680 --> 06:26.671
But it does make us...

06:27.850 --> 06:30.012
unforgettable.

06:46.640 --> 06:47.596
- Hey.

06:47.640 --> 06:48.766
(Clears throat)

06:48.800 --> 06:50.768
- Hey. How's your...

06:50.810 --> 06:53.108
