06:53.140 --> 06:55.006
- Oh, not bad.

06:55.040 --> 06:57.179
Fender-bender, enema.

06:57.210 --> 06:58.746
Same old.

06:58.780 --> 07:00.578
- Well, I hope
the two weren't related.

07:00.620 --> 07:02.349
- So, they sent
Mr. Calambey home?

07:02.380 --> 07:05.680
His burns healed nicely.
- Yeah! Minor miracle.

07:05.720 --> 07:08.610
I'm not going anywhere near
my deep fryer anytime soon!

07:08.660 --> 07:10.185
- How can you even
own one of those?

07:10.230 --> 07:12.858
