- Oh no, I was...

07:12.900 --> 07:14.390
No, I was kidding.

07:14.430 --> 07:19.459
I was kidding. Although I'm not
past torching a brule on occasion.

07:19.500 --> 07:22.606
Because men enjoy...

07:22.640 --> 07:24.165
torching things.

07:24.840 --> 07:26.877
(Clears throat)

07:26.910 --> 07:28.605
- So, you like to cook?

07:28.640 --> 07:34.477
- Yeah, I always thought it would be
my other profession if I didn't go into...

07:34.520 --> 07:36.045
Um...

07:36.080 --> 07:40.153
So, I'm in this
rehabilitation program.

07:40.190 --> 07:41.214
- Oh!
- Yeah.

07:41.260 --> 07:42.955
Trying to prove
to Nora Sorgent,

07:42.990 --> 07:45.550
I'm an upstanding
member of society

07:45.590 --> 07:48.321
and not a raging ass hat.

07:48.360 --> 07:51.330
- Hmm. That must be
a New program.

07:51.370 --> 07:52.633
- Is.
- How's it going?

07:52.670 --> 07:54.764
- Decent. Yeah.

07:54.800 --> 07:57.906
Although I'm not really
putting in the effort that I'd like.

07:57.940 --> 07:59.874
- Oh, well,
one day at a time.

07:59.910 --> 08:01.002
(Laughing)

08:02.750 --> 08:05.845
- Yeah. Uh, so...

08:05.880 --> 08:09.111
I was wondering
if maybe you...

08:09.150 --> 08:15.749
if maybe you might want to eat
sometime. Uh, wow, like tomorrow.

08:15.790 --> 08:18.020
Because you're not
working the night shift,

08:18.060 --> 08:19.221
and, hey, neither am I.

08:19.260 --> 08:21.649
So what a serendipitous...

08:21.700 --> 08:23.759
bit of scheduling.

08:23.800 --> 08:26.292
- Well, I do need to eat.

08:28.670 --> 08:30.729
See you later,
dough eyes.

08:40.980 --> 08:42.072
- Well, that was fast.

08:42.120 --> 08:44.316
I told Rebecca
you'd be another day.

08:44.350 --> 08:46.887
I thought you'd wanna
watch it a few more times.

08:46.920 --> 08:48.581
- Can I talk to you alone?

08:50.060 --> 08:51.721
- I'm fine here.

08:51.760 --> 08:53.159
- Really?

08:53.200 --> 08:54.429
A porno?

08:54.460 --> 08:56.326
That's your big move?

08:56.360 --> 09:00.934
- Bishop likes to think of it
as a video postcard of sorts.

09:00.970 --> 09:02.563
"Wish you were here."

09:04.140 --> 09:05.767
- What are you doing?

09:05.810 --> 09:07.278
- What?

09:07.310 --> 09:09.745
You didn't like it?

09:09.780 --> 09:11.578
- Bishop knows
where I stand.

09:11.610 --> 09:13.977
A pathetic snuff film
isn't gonna change my mind.

09:14.020 --> 09:15.579
- Fair enough.

09:17.250 --> 09:19.582
Give it back,
and I'll dispose of it.

09:21.790 --> 09:23.121
Ah!

09:23.160 --> 09:25.219
You kept it!

09:26.260 --> 09:28.297
- So you do miss me.

09:30.300 --> 09:32.064
- Don't do that.

09:33.440 --> 09:34.999
You...

09:35.040 --> 09:37.668
You don't want me back.

09:37.710 --> 09:40.509
You ever thought of
what might happen?

09:40.540 --> 09:43.749
- Yes, it's all I think about. It's
all any of us think about, really.

09:43.780 --> 09:47.546
- You would be nothing...

09:47.580 --> 09:51.312
all over again,
and you know it.

09:51.350 --> 09:53.409
- Yap, yap, Yap.

09:53.460 --> 09:56.418
You and all the little doggies!

09:57.330 --> 09:59.890
(Barking)

10:01.160 --> 10:02.559
(Door closing)

10:02.600 --> 10:05.069
I thought you had
a hold over him.

10:05.100 --> 10:09.594
I guess I was wrong.
- It would have been fine if you weren't here.

10:09.640 --> 10:12.007
I can do it.
- That's what you keep saying!

10:12.040 --> 10:13.337
And yet...

10:13.380 --> 10:14.905
- Is it true what they say

10:14.940 --> 10:16.271
about Aidan and Bishop?

10:16.310 --> 10:19.439
- They weren't gods.

10:21.850 --> 10:23.716
Are you in love with him?

10:26.090 --> 10:27.910
- What would be the point?

10:38.470 --> 10:39.938
(Door closing)

10:39.970 --> 10:41.893
(Sirens in distance)

10:45.670 --> 10:47.308
(Footsteps approaching)

10:47.340 --> 10:48.774
- Ahh...

10:48.810 --> 10:50.300
