11:47.670 --> 11:50.002
be someone's boyfriend again.

11:50.770 --> 11:52.772
Share a paper, see a movie.

11:52.810 --> 11:54.130
- Sounds like retirement.

11:54.180 --> 11:57.480
Is sex in this equation?

11:59.050 --> 12:00.449
- What?

12:05.550 --> 12:06.915
Emily...

12:06.960 --> 12:10.828
- (Crying): I'm sorry. I just
didn't know where else to go.

12:25.210 --> 12:28.032
- So, what brings you here?

12:28.080 --> 12:31.448
- How about:
"Are you OK, Emily?"

12:31.480 --> 12:34.040
- Are you...
Are you OK, Emily?

12:34.080 --> 12:36.720
- I know you don't wanna see me.
OK? I get it.

12:38.750 --> 12:40.514
Jackie and I broke up.

12:40.560 --> 12:41.789
- Oh...

12:41.820 --> 12:43.356
That's rough.

12:43.390 --> 12:44.152
- Thank you.

12:44.190 --> 12:46.557
And I can't keep
living in there,

12:46.590 --> 12:50.026
and it's too late to
find a roommate this semester.

12:50.070 --> 12:51.629
- So...

12:51.670 --> 12:53.536
- I need a place to crash, OK?

12:53.570 --> 12:56.039
- Uh, OK, see, I--
- Aidan's OK with it.

12:56.070 --> 12:58.129
Right?

12:59.410 --> 13:01.879
- She's your sister.

13:03.350 --> 13:05.045
(Sighs)

13:05.080 --> 13:09.472
- How long?
- Just till I get back on my feet.

13:13.960 --> 13:16.383
Can I have this cookie?

