16:42.530 --> 16:44.464
What do people like to eat?

16:44.500 --> 16:46.127
What do we, the people,

16:46.170 --> 16:48.138
like to eat?

16:53.180 --> 16:54.670
- Aidan's hot.

16:54.710 --> 16:56.109
(Laughing)

16:56.140 --> 16:58.450
Sometimes I wish
I was into that.

16:58.480 --> 17:00.619
Jackie would so freak!

17:00.650 --> 17:02.618
- Yeah, you don't wanna...

17:02.650 --> 17:05.950
That is complicated.

17:05.990 --> 17:09.153
- Um, yeah,
part of the appeal!

17:10.829 --> 17:13.390
How's things going
on your front?

17:14.430 --> 17:16.296
- Oh, good.

17:16.329 --> 17:17.798
Work's good.

17:17.829 --> 17:20.834
- Girls, Josh. Life.

17:20.869 --> 17:23.430
Are you OK?

17:25.210 --> 17:28.840
